Subject: [PATCH 5.12 501/677] HID: lenovo: Map mic-mute button to KEY_F20 instead of KEY_MICMUTE
Date:   Wed, 12 May 2021 16:49:07 +0200
Message-Id: <20210512144854.030898625@linuxfoundation.org>
